<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Monaco', 'Menlo', 'Ubuntu Mono', monospace;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0a0a0a 0%, #1a1a2e 50%, #16213e 100%);
            color: #e0e0e0;
            min-height: 100vh;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        
        header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            padding: 20px 0;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #333;
        }
        
        h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #4fc3f7, #29b6f6, #03a9f4);
            background-clip: text;
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        nav {
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        
        nav ul {
            list-style: none;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 30px;
        }
        
        nav a {
            color: #e0e0e0;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border: 1px solid #333;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        nav a:hover,
        nav a.active {
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #4fc3f7, #29b6f6);
            color: #000;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        
        main {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 30px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }
        
        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 0;
            color: #888;
            border-top: 1px solid #333;
            margin-top: 40px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <h1>üåû 6ol Core</h1>
            <p>Embodied Presence ¬∑ Web Dashboard</p>
            <nav>
                <ul>
                    <li><a href="/" class="<%= page === 'home' ? 'active' : '' %>">Home</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/maps" class="<%= page === 'maps' ? 'active' : '' %>">Spirit Maps</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/reflections" class="<%= page === 'reflections' ? 'active' : '' %>">Reflections</a></li>
                </ul>
            </nav>
        </header>
        
        <main>
            <div class="welcome-section">
                <h2>üåü Welcome to 6ol Core</h2>
                <p>This is the central hub for embodied presence and spiritual exploration.</p>
                
                <div class="features-grid" style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 20px; margin: 30px 0;">
                    <div class="feature-card" style="background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);">
                        <h3>üó∫Ô∏è Spirit Maps</h3>
                        <p>Navigate through the landscape of consciousness and spiritual territories.</p>
                        <a href="/maps" style="color: #4fc3f7; text-decoration: none;">Explore Maps ‚Üí</a>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="feature-card" style="background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);">
                        <h3>üí≠ Reflections</h3>
                        <p>Deep contemplations and insights from the journey of embodied presence.</p>
                        <a href="/reflections" style="color: #4fc3f7; text-decoration: none;">Read Reflections ‚Üí</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="status-section" style="margin-top: 40px; padding: 20px; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3); border-radius: 8px;">
                    <h3>üîÑ Current Status</h3>
                    <p><strong>Phase:</strong> Layer-3 Web Dashboard</p>
                    <p><strong>Focus:</strong> Embodied Presence Integration</p>
                    <p><strong>Version:</strong> v1.0.0</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </main>
        
        <footer>
            <p>&copy; 2024 6ol Core ¬∑ Phase 3: Web Dashboard</p>
        </footer>
    </div>
</body>
</html>